author: Dana Rubinstein, Anna Gronewold and Arek Sarkissian
title: New York's snowbirds, super-rich could stymie attempts to seal Florida borders
description: Florida's governor wants to keep New Yorkers out, but they've already arrived.
content:
A Florida beach | Getty Images | Getty Images
